  {
    "@id": "https://niagarasymphony.com/event/pastorale-2/",
    "http://ogp.me/ns#locale": [
      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "en_US"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#type": [
      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "article"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "Pastorale - Niagara Symphony"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-us",
        "@value": "Join us for an evening of musical masterpieces, where the human spirit soars and the beauty of nature unfolds. Feel the triumph as Beethoven’s Fidelio Overture bursts forth. Witness the composer’s struggle and ultimate victory in crafting the perfect opening to his only opera, a testament to resilience and artistic passion. Be swept away by the serene beauty of Copland's Appalachian Spring. Experience the joy and tranquility of a wedding day in rural Pennsylvania, as the music paints a vivid picture of dawn's gentle awakening and the peaceful close of day. Immerse yourself in the pastoral splendor of Beethoven's Symphony No. 6, \"Pastorale.\" Feel the composer's deep love for nature as the music evokes the sights, sounds, and emotions of a day in the countryside. Let the symphony's expressive melodies and evocative textures transport you to a world of tranquility and beauty. Don't miss this opportunity to experience the power and beauty of these timeless works. Let the music ignite your senses and stir your soul."
      }
    ],
