        "@value": "Holiday Magic: A Festive Celebration!   Join us for a heartwarming holiday concert filled with all your favorite carols, performed by a full orchestra and choir in a sparkling seasonal spectacular!  Sing along to timeless classics, feel the joy of live music, and don’t miss a special visit from Santa Claus himself - perfect for the whole family!  Music, magic, and holiday cheer - come make memories that will last all year!"
      }
    ],
